  <verse number="10" style="v" />You are witnesses, and God also, how holy, righteously, and blamelessly we behaved ourselves toward you who believe.

  <verse number="11" style="v" />In the same way, you know how with each one of you, as a father with his own children, we exhorted and encouraged you. We testified

  <verse number="12" style="v" />that you should walk in a manner that is worthy of God, who calls you into his own kingdom and glory.</para>
